value.0: This ranger looks like he is the leader of this small village. His eyes appear ever watchful and his face shows that he is prepared to guard this village at any moment's notice.
The people of Thundertree seem distrustful of strangers, as it should be - there is not much reason to visit a quaint little town such as this.
